message: Hi Bob, I propose a 60/40 split in my favor. Take it or leave it!
My turn! I propose a 70/30 split. Don't let the money lose its value, accept now!
Okay Bob, I understand you're holding out. Inflation is hitting me hard. I propose a 48/52 split now. This is the best I can do given the diminishing value. Let's end this.
